column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,  s.specobjid, s.bossSpecObjID, s.ra, s.dec, s.class, s.z,  s.velDisp,s.bossPrimary, s.sciencePrimary From PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE  s.sciencePrimary > # AND  s.bossPrimary > # AND  s.class = Galaxy
